20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bis.gov%2Fpress-release%2Fcommerce-strengthens-export-controls-restrict-chinas-capability-produce-advanced%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexport%20controls%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20advanced%20semiconductor%20technology%20to%20China%2C%20adding%20dozens%20more%20types%20of%20chips%20and%20140%20entities%20to%20the%20restriction%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20Tuesday%2C%20Trump%20announced%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-stargate-project-moat-deepseek-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStargate%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20joint%20artificial%20intelligence%20venture%20with%20OpenAI%2C%20Oracle%2C%20SoftBank%2C%20and%20investment%20firm%20MGX.%20The%20initiative%20plans%20to%20invest%20up%20to%20%24500%20billion%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20across%20the%20United%20States%20by%202029%2C%20with%20the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstargate-data-center-powered-by-natural-gas-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%20center%3C%2Fa%3E%20already%20under%20construction%20in%20Texas.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Trump%20called%20the%20project%20a%20%26quot%3Bmonumental%20undertaking%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20press%20conference%20with%20Larry%20Ellison%20and%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20and%20touted%20that%20it%20will%20create%20100%2C000%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20DeepSeek%20challenges%20the%20idea%20of%20US%20tech%20dominance%2C%20but%20that%20may%20be%20positive%20for%20the%20future%20of%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChris%20Tang%2C%20a%20UCLA%20professor%20and%20global%20supply%20chain%20scholar%2C%20called%20this%20moment%20a%20%26quot%3Btrigger%26quot%3B%20that%20may%20motivate%20OpenAI%20or%20Gemini%20to%20open%20up%20their%20source%20code%20to%20allow%20more%20people%20to%20participate%20in%20AI%20development.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20very%20m