g%20a%20free%20account%20via%20the%20web%2C%20mobile%20app%2C%20or%20API.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222b1ab0a5-aaee-4007-a254-2a34e6ae8fcb%5C%22%3EWhy%20are%20investors%20worried%20about%20DeepSeek%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20R1%20model%20is%20built%20on%20its%20V3%20base%20model.%20The%20company%20has%20said%20the%20V3%20model%20was%20trained%20on%20around%202%2C000%20Nvidia%20H800%20chips%20at%20an%20overall%20cost%20of%20roughly%20%245.6%20million.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20though%20the%20training%20costs%20are%20only%20one%20part%20of%20the%20equation%2C%20that's%20still%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20other%20top%20companies%20are%20spending%20to%20develop%20their%20own%20foundational%20AI%20models.%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%2C%20for%20example%2C%20announced%20that%20Meta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-meta-ai-investment-capital-expenditure-datacenter-deepseek-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplans%20to%20spend%20over%20%2460%20billion%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20capital%20expenditures%20this%20year%20as%20it%20doubles%20down%20on%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Bernstein%20analysts%2C%20DeepSeek's%20model%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexplaining-deepseek-chinese-models-efficiency-scaring-markets-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E20%20to%2040%20times%20cheaper%20to%20run%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20similar%20models%20from%20OpenAI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relatively%20low%20stated%20cost%20of%20DeepSeek's%20latest%20model%20%E2%80%94%20combined%20with%20its%20impressive%20capability%20%E2%80%94%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Silicon%20Valley%20strategy%20of%20investing%20billions%20into%20data%20centers%20and%20AI%20infrastructure%20to%20train%20up%20new%20models%20with%20the%20latest%20chips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%2C%20a%20company%20that%20produces%20the%20high-powered%20chips%20crucial%20to%20powering%20AI%20models%2C%20saw%20its%20s