imated%20they%20built%20and%20trained%20the%20model%20using%202%2C000%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ENvidia%20H800%20chips%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20under%20%246%20million%2C%20significantly%20less%20than%20many%20of%20its%20AI%20competitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EX%20owner%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20said%20his%20platform's%20AI%20chatbot%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-hints-how-much-grok-ai-chatbot-training-costs-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGrok%203%20is%20training%20on%20100%2C000%20of%20Nvidia's%20H100%20GPUs.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Meta%20CEO%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20said%20last%20January%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-ai-flex-meta-nvidia-gpus-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20would%20purchase%20350%2C000%20Nvidia%20H100%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20then%20stunned%20Silicon%20Valley%20again%20with%20the%20launch%20of%20its%20R1%20model%20on%20January%2020%2C%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b7ce561-8d43-4079-879d-629b8fb4c61f%5C%22%3EWenfeng'%20approach%20to%20running%20DeepSeek%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWenfeng%20said%20in%20the%202024%20interview%20that%20his%20main%20focus%20for%20DeepSeek%20is%20researching%20large%20models%20and%20achieving%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-agi-artificial-general-intelligence-explained-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartificial%20general%20intelligence%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20principle%20is%20neither%20to%20sell%20at%20a%20loss%20nor%20to%20seek%20excessive%20profits.%20The%20current%20pricing%20allows%20for%20a%20modest%20profit%20margin%20above%20our%20costs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthechinaacademy.org%2Finterview-with-deepseek-founder-were-done-following-its-time-to-lead%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20translated%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20said%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-yann-lecun-deepseek-open-source-openai-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20company%20%26quot%3Bwon't%20go%20closed-source%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20establishing%20a%20robust%20technology%20ecosystem%20matters%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWenfeng%20says%20China's%20AI%20industry%20has%20been%20playing%20catch-up%20with%20the%20US%2C%20and%20he%20wants%20DeepSeek%20to%20change%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20China's%20AI%20cannot%20remain%20a%20follower%20forever.%20Often%2C%20we%20say%20there's%20a%20one-%20or%20two-year%20gap%20between%20Chinese%20and%20American%20AI%2C%20but%20the%20real%20gap%20is%20between%20originality%20and%20imitation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20translated%20interview.%20%26quot%3BIf%20this%20doesn't%20change%2C%20China%20will%20always%20be%20a%20follower.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-deepseek-founder-liang-wenfeng%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1738012645000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6797eb57196626c40985283e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-deepseek-founder-liang-wenfeng%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Liang%20Wenfeng%20is%20the%20founder%20of%20DeepSeek%2C%20the%20Chinese%20AI%20startup%20potentially%20upending%20the%20industry.%20Here's%20everything%20to%20know%20about%20the%20hedge%20funder.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sjackson%40insider.com%20(Sarah%20Jackson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A79%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-deepseek-founder-liang-wenfeng%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20asks%20federal%20agencies%20to%20make%20RTO%2