rk%20together%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20our%20people%20and%20towards%20global%20peace%2C%20prosperity%2C%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20posted%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20conversation%20between%20both%20leaders%20since%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20began%20his%20second%20term%20last%20Monday%20with%20a%20flurry%20of%20executive%20actions%20aimed%20at%20overhauling%20US%20immigration%2C%20and%20the%20H1-B%20visas%20that%20allow%20companies%20to%20bring%20foreigners%20with%20specific%20qualifications%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20among%20the%20largest%20sources%20of%20legal%20migration%20into%20the%20United%20States%2C%20but%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Indians%20have%20also%20entered%20the%20country%20illegally%20in%20recent%20years%20by%20crossing%20the%20Canadian%20and%20Mexican%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20prepared%20to%20take%20back%20its%20citizens%20residing%20illegally%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20foreign%20minister%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20after%20meeting%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20in%20Washington%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20Trump's%20inauguration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20Indian%20talent%20and%20Indian%20skills%20to%20have%20the%20maximum%20opportunity%20at%20the%20global%20level.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20we%20are%20also%20very%20firmly%20opposed%20to%20illegal%20mobility%20and%20illegal%20migration%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jaishankar%2C%20who%20attended%20Trump's%20inauguration%2C%20said%20Wednesday%20responding%20to%20a%20query%20on%20news%20reports%20that%20India%20was%20working%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20the%20deportation%20of%20around%2018%2C000%20Indians%20who%20are%20either%20undocumented%2C%20or%20have%20overstayed%20their%20visas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20with%20every%20country%2C%20and%20the%20US%20is%20no%20exception%2C%20we%20have%20always%20taken%20the%20view%20that%20if%20any%20of%20our%20citizens%20are%20here%20illegally%2C%20and%20if%20we%20are%20sure%20that%20they%20are%20our%20citizens%2C%20we%20have%20always%20been%20open%20to%20their%20legitimate%20return%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Rubio%20had%20%26quot%3Bemphasized%20the%20Trump%20administration's%20desire%20to%20work%20with%20India%20to%20advance%20economic%20ties%20and%20address%20concerns%20related%20to%20irregular%20migration%2C%26quot%3B%20State%20Department%20spokesperson%20Tammy%20Bruce%20said%20in%20a%20readout%20after%20Tuesday's%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20said%20India%20is%20looking%20for%20%26quot%3Bbolder%2C%20bigger%20and%20a%20more%20ambitious%26quot%3B%20relationship%20with%20the%20US%20and%20indicated%20its%20readiness%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Trump%20administration%20to%20address%20issues%20like%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20US%20census%20showed%20its%20Indian-origin%20population%20had%20grown%20by%2050%20per%20cent%20to%204.8%20million%20in%20the%20decade%20to%202020%2C%20while%20more%20than%20a%20third%20of%20the%20nearly%201.3%20million%20Indian%20students%20studying%20abroad%20in%202022%20were%20in%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737999120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F9pufioj_pm-modi-trump-afp_650x400_27_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-modi-speaks-to-trump-days-after-us-presidents-inauguration-sources-7572191%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20Monday%20held%20a%20telephonic%20conversation%20with%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20a%20week%20after%20his%20inauguration%20as%20US%20President%2C%20and%20congratulated%20his%20%26quot%3Bdear%20friend%20on%20his%20hist