ies%2C%20according%20to%20local%20emergency%20management%20agencies.%20While%20rare%20in%20the%20region%2C%20minor%20earthquakes%20occur%20in%20New%20England%20annually.%20Residents%20reported%20feeling%20strong%20shaking%2C%20but%20operations%20and%20infrastructure%20remained%20unaffected.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fearthquake-rattles-houses-in-maine-and-is-felt-hundreds-of-miles-away%2Farticleshow%2F117609867.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fearthquake-rattles-houses-in-maine-and-is-felt-hundreds-of-miles-away%2Famp_articleshow%2F117609867.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fearthquake-rattles-houses-in-maine-and-is-felt-hundreds-of-miles-away%2Famp_articleshow%2F117609867.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BMuster%20Courage...%26quot%3B%3A%20Top%20Court%20Raps%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20For%20Denying%20Bail%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bgood%20reason%26quot%3B%20to%20decline%20bail%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rapped%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20for%20failing%20to%20show%20%26quot%3Bcourage%26quot%3B%20in%20granting%20bail%20to%20a%20cleric%20in%20an%20alleged%20conversion%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can%20understand%20that%20the%20trial%20court%20declined%20bail%20as%20trial%20courts%20seldom%20muster%20the%20courage%20of%20granting%20bail%2C%20be%20it%20any%20offence.%20However%2C%20at%20least%2C%20it%20was%20expected%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20to%20muster%20the%20courage%20and%20exercise%20its%20discretion%20judiciously%2C%26quot%3B%20observed%20the%20bench%20of%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20R%20Mahadevan%2C%20granting%20bail%20to%20the%20cleric%20arrested%20under%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Prohibition%20of%20Unlawful%20Conversion%20of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscretion%2C%20said%20the%20top%20court%2C%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20judge%20on%20his%20own%20whims%20and%20fancy%20declines%20bail%20saying%20conversion%20is%20something%20very%20serious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20conscious%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20grant%20of%20bail%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20discretion.%20But%20discretion%20has%20to%20be%20exercised%20judicially%20keeping%20in%20mind%20the%20well%20settled%20principles%20of%20grant%20of%20bail.%20Discretion%20does%20not%20mean%20that%20the%20judge%20on%20his%20own%20whims%20and%20fancy%20declines%20bail%20saying%20conversion%20is%20something%20very%20serious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20underlined%20that%20every%20year%20so%20many%20conferences%2C%20seminars%2C%20workshops%20etc.%20are%20held%20to%20make%20the%20trial%20judges%20understand%20how%20to%20exercise%20their%20discretion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20top%20court's%20notice%20that%20the%C2%A0child%20being%20mentally%20challenged%20was%20abandoned%20by%20the%20parents%20and%20was%20thrown%20on%20the%20streets%20and%20the%20cleric%2C%20who%20has%20no%20prior%20criminal%20record%2C%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%20brought%20the%20child%20to%20his%20place%20and%20gave%20him%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20High%20Court%20should%20have%20exercised%20its%20discretion%20by%20granting%20bail%20to%20the%20petitioner.%20There%20was%20no%20good%20reason%20for%20the%20High%20Court%20to%20decline%20bail.%20The%20offence%20alleged%20is%20not%20that%20serious%20or%20grave%20like%20murder%2C%20dacoity%2C%20rape%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%20when%20the%20High%20Court%20declines%20bail%20in%20the%20matters%20of%20the%20present%20type%2C%20it%20gives%20an%20impression%20that%20altogether%20different%20considerations%20weighed%20with%20the%20presiding%20officer%20ignoring%20the%20well%20settled%20principles%20of%20grant%20of%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20the%20cleric%20should%20not%20now%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20the%20trial%2C%20cautioned%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlagging%20it%20as%20a%20cautionary%20tale%20for%20case%20pendency%20in%20courts%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20the%20High%20Courts%20and%20now%20unfortunately%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20the%20country%20is%20flooded%20with%20bail%20applications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20matter%20should%20not%20have%20reached%20up%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20The%20trial%20court%20itself%20should%20have%20been%20courageous%20enough%20to%20exercise%20its%20discretion%20and%20release%20the%20petitioner%20on%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20lamented%20the%20top%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737997440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F01n469u8_supreme-court-of-india_625x300_12_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-raps-allahabad-high-court-over-bail-denial-in-conversion-case-7573423%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noting%20that%20there%20was%20no%20%26quot%3Bgood%20reason%26quot%3B%20to%20decline%20bail%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20rapped%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20for%20failing%20to%20show%20%26quot%3Bcourage%26quot%3B%20in%20granting%20bail%20to%20a%20cleric%20in%20an%20alleged%20conversion%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Federal%20Bank's%20Q3FY25%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20down%205%25%20at%20Rs%20955%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737997196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2