en%20as%20a%20big%20step%20in%20this%20direction.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20yatra--%20which%20involves%20a%20visit%20to%20mount%20Kailash%20and%20Mansarovar%20lake%20in%20Tibet%20--%20has%20been%20suspended%20since%20the%20Covid%20outbreak%20of%202020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPost-Covid%2C%20there%20was%20no%20renewal%20of%20arrangements%20by%20the%20Chinese%20side%20amid%20prickly%20relations%20between%20Beijing%20and%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20situation%20escalated%20after%20the%20Galwan%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meet%20also%20agreed%20in%20principle%20to%20resume%20direct%20air%20services%20between%20the%20two%20countries%3B%20the%20relevant%20technical%20authorities%20on%20the%20two%20sides%20will%20meet%20and%20negotiate%20an%20updated%20framework%20for%20this%20purpose%20at%20an%20early%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20early%20meeting%20of%20the%20India-China%20Expert%20Level%20Mechanism%20will%20also%20be%20held%20to%20discuss%20resumption%20of%20provision%20of%20hydrological%20data%20and%20other%20cooperation%20pertaining%20to%20trans-border%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20visit%2C%20the%20Foreign%20Secretary%20called%20on%20Member%20of%20the%20Politburo%20of%20the%20Central%20Committee%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%2C%20Director%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20Central%20Commission%20of%20Foreign%20Affairs%20and%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%2C%20and%20Minister%20of%20the%20International%20Department%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%20Liu%20Jianchao%2C%20the%20ministry%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737990600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-09%2Fkailash-mansarovar-yatra_650x400_71443596661.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-china-decide-to-resume-kailash-mansarovar-yatra-this-summer-7572461%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20and%20China%20held%20a%20two-day%20foreign%20secretary-level%20talks%20in%20which%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20resume%