2F9vra7hi_mig-29-indian-air-force_625x300_07_October_18.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Csmall%3ERepresentational%20image%20of%20a%20MiG-29%20operated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%2C%20flying%20at%20very%20high%20speed%2C%20was%20exposed%20to%20temperatures%20of%20-%2040%20degrees%20Celsius.%20There%20were%20dangers%20of%20hypoxia%20and%20sickness.%20He%20quickly%20took%20control%20of%20the%20aircraft%20while%20flying%20on%20head-down%20instruments%20-%20the%20displays%20located%20on%20the%20cockpit%20panel%20-%20as%20opposed%20to%20HUD%20which%20projects%20information%20on%20the%20windshield.%20Flight%20Lt%20Aman%20announced%20an%20emergency%20using%20standby%20radio%20control%20and%20ensured%20the%20safety%20of%20any%20civil%20aircraft%20flying%20in%20the%20proximity.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20descended%20to%20an%20altitude%20of%203%20kilometres%20from%208%20when%20the%20canopy%20blew%20off%20and%20landed%20at%20the%20nearest%20airbase%20with%20no%20radio%20reception%20and%20severe%20pain%20in%20the%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJanuary%2025%2C%202025%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlight%20Lt%20Aman%20Singh%20Hans%20avoided%20a%20catastrophe.%20He%20saved%20the%20aircraft%20and%20landed%20safely.%20For%20displaying%20indomitable%20valour%20and%20exemplary%20gallantry%20beyond%20the%20call%20of%20duty%26quot%3B%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20awarded%20him%20a%20Shaurya%20Chakra%20-%20the%20third%20highest%20peacetime%20gallantry%20award%20-%20on%20Republic%20Day%20this%20year.%20Flight%20Lieutenant%20Hans%20is%20among%20eight%20personnel%20awarded%20the%20prestigious%20gallantry%20medal%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20the%20Republic%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%20was%20commissioned%20into%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20in%202019%20and%20since%202020%2C%20he%20has%20been%20flying%20the%20MiG-29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMiG-29%2C%20NATO%20name%20'Fulcrum'%20and%20Indian%20name%20'Baaz'%2C%20is%20an%20air%20superiority%20fighter%20jet%20originating%20in%20Soviet%20Russia.%20It%20was%20formally%20inducted%20into%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20in%201987%2C%20initially%20with%20two%20squadrons%20-%20No.%2028%20and%20No.%2047%20Squadrons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Not%20The%20First%20Time'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20have%20been%20three%20known%20incidents%20including%20the%20one%20on%20March%2028%20last%20year%20when%20a%20MiG-29's%20canopy%20blew%20off%20mid-air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%201%2C%202016%2C%20Squadron%20Leader%20Rijul%20Sharma%20was%20authorised%20to%20fly%20an%20air%20sortie%20in%20a%20MiG%2029%20fighter%20jet%20to%20test%20the%20aircraft%20at%20supersonic%20speeds%20at%20a%20height%20of%2010%20Km.%20While%20conducting%20the%20'Supersonic%20Flying%20Corridor'%2C%20he%20was%20110%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20air%20base%20he%20took%20off%20at%20Mach%201.1%20or%201%2C200%20km%2Fhr%2C%20and%20the%20canopy%20of%20the%20aircraft%20shattered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fggnof6t_squadron-leader-rijul-sharma_625x300_27_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Csmall%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ESquadron%20Leader%20Rijul%20Sharma%3Cbr%3E%5CnPhoto%20Credit%3A%20www.bharat-rakshak.com%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsmall%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20led%20to%20explosive%20decompression%20of%20the%20glass%20pieces%20of%20the%20canopy%20hitting%20the%20shoulder%20of%20the%20pilot.%20He%20was%20exposed%20to%20extremely%20low%20temperatures%20of%20minus%2028%20degrees%20Celsius%20and%20a%20very%20severe%20wind%20blast%20due%20to%20supersonic%20speed.%20His%20right%20shoulder%20was%20severely%20injured%20but%20the%20pilot%20managed%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20the%20aircraft%20and%20descended%20to%20an%20altitude%20of%203%20kilometres%20at%20the%20same%20time%20reduced%20speed%20for%20effective%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pilot%20managed%20to%20land%20safely%20and%20avoided%20any%20catastrophe.%20He%20managed%20to%20avert%20any%20disaster%20since%20he%20was%20flying%20to%20a%20petrochemical%20factory.%20Squadron%20Leader%20Rijul%20Sharma%20was%20awarded%20the%20Vayu%20Sena%20Medal%20(Gallantry).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Chief%20of%20Air%20Staff%2C%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20VR%20Chaudhari%2C%20who%20was%20a%20Squadron%20Leader%20in%201994%2C%20shared%20an%20incident%20when%20his%20MiG-29's%20%26quot%3Bcanopy%20flew%20off%26quot%3B%20at%20Mach%201.9%20speed%20(almost%20two%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findias-most-fearless-3-service-chiefs-recall-biggest-challenges-faced-in-career-101674039457476.html%5C%22%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20book%20%3C%2Fa%3E'India's%20Most%20Fearless%203'%20Air%20Chief%20Marshal%20Chaudhari%20shared%20the%20incident%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20conducting%20an%20air%20test%20on%20the%20MiG-29%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20his%20canopy%20%26quot%3Bflew%20off%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20time%20of%20useful%20consciousness%20in%20such%20a%20situation%20and%20the%20time%20left%20after%20explosive%20decompression%20at%20such%20an%20altitude%20and%20speed%20-%20was%20only%20six%20seconds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fcrbf4ldo_indian-air-force-chief-air-chief-marshal-vr-chaudhari_625x300_27_March_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwid