C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20arrangements%20for%20the%20game%2C%20Sharma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20know%20Virat's%20presence%20raises%20the%20profile%20of%20the%20match.%20Normally%2C%20we%20have%2010%20to%2012%20private%20security%20personnel%20for%20a%20regular%20Ranji%20match%2C%20but%20we%20will%20definitely%20increase%20security%20so%20that%20Virat%20can%20train%20without%20any%20disturbance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20also%20informed%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20about%20the%20match.%26quot%3B%20While%20Ranji%20matches%20are%20free%20for%20spectators%20but%20they%20usually%20open%20one%20stand%20but%20for%20this%20match%2C%20DDCA%20will%20open%20three%20stands%20at%20the%20Ambedkar%20Stadium%20End.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGate%20Nos.%207%2C%2015%2C%20and%2016%20will%20be%20open%20to%20the%20public.%20We%20will%20arrange%20for%20drinking%20water%2C%20and%20the%20toilets%20will%20be%20clean%20and%20hygienic.%20Come%20and%20enjoy%20the%20match.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20will%20be%20security%20checks%20before%20allowing%20the%20public%20to%20enter%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20live%20telecast%20or%20streaming%20as%20of%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kohli's%20presence%20makes%20the%20Delhi%20versus%20Railways%20match%20the%20most%20high-profile%20domestic%20game%20in%20recent%20past%2C%20there%20is%20some%20bad%20news%20for%20fans%20as%20there%20is%20currently%20no%20provision%20for%20broadcasting%20the%20marquee%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20if%20BCCI%20will%20make%20any%20last%20minute%20arrangements%20since%20Kohli%20is%20playing%20but%20we%20haven't%20been%20intimated%20anything%20about%20broadcast%20of%20this%20game.%20Normally%20all%20big%20centres%20get%20one%20live%20game%20allotted%20(TV%20or%20streaming).%20We%20had%20a%20game%20against%20Tamil%20Nadu%20which%20was%20aired%20live.%20The%20roster%20for%20broadcast%20is%20set%20months%20in%20advance%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20DDCA%20official%20in%20the%20know%20of%20things%20told%20PTI%20on%20conditions%20of%20anonymity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20live%20telecast%20Mumbai%20vs%20J%26amp%3BK%20game%20was%20taken%20much%20earlier%20and%20it%20was%20coincidental%20that%20India%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20rising%20star%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112646-yashasvi-jaiswal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EYashasvi%20Jaiswal%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20part%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20next%20round%2C%20the%20main%20match%20that%20will%20be%20televised%20as%20well%20as%20live-streamed%20is%20Karnataka%20versus%20Haryana%20at%20Chinnaswamy.%20Two%20more%20matches%20will%20be%20streamed.%20One%20of%20those%20is%20Bengal%20vs%20Punjab%20at%20Eden%20Gardens.%20There%20is%20a%20streaming%20of%20a%20third%20match%20but%20as%20of%20now%20it%20doesn't%20involve%20Delhi%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20BCCI%20official%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20the%20BCCI%20decides%20to%20make%20arrangements%20for%20live%20streaming%20in%20the%20next%2048%20hours%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20logistical%20challenge%2C%20requiring%20a%20multi-camera%20setup%20and%20the%20delegation%20of%20a%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESquad%3A%20Ayush%20Badoni%20(captain)%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Pranav%20Rajvanshi%20(wk)%2C%20Sanat%20Sangwan%2C%20Arpit%20Rana%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mayank%20Gusain%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F122390-mayank-gusain-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMayank%20Gusain%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Shivam%20Sharma%2C%20Sumit%20Mathur%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vansh%20Bedi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F122342-vansh-bedi-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVansh%20Bedi%