ussian%20fighter%20jets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Iran%20and%20Russia%20also%20signed%20a%20comprehensive%20strategic%20partnership%20which%20did%20not%20mention%20arms%20transfers%20but%20said%20the%20two%20will%20develop%20their%20%26quot%3Bmilitary-technical%20cooperation.%26quot%3B%20The%20deal%20reinforced%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20just%20as%20they%20are%20both%20facing%20mounting%20geopolitical%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2020-year%20deal%20was%20signed%20by%20Iranian%20President%20Masoud%20Pezeshkian%20and%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20Moscow.%20It%20includes%20a%20clause%20that%20neither%20country%20would%20allow%20its%20territory%20to%20be%20used%20for%20any%20action%20that%20would%20threaten%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20other%2C%20nor%20provide%20any%20help%20to%20any%20party%20attacking%20either%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20deal%20was%20in%20talks%20for%20years%2C%20but%20current%20geopolitical%20events%20made%20it%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour.%20While%20Russia's%20regional%20standing%20has%20been%20strained%20due%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Iran%20has%20been%20grappling%20with%20Western%20sanctions%20and%20the%20weakening%20of%20several%20regional%20allies%20amid%20conflict%20with%20Israel%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20arguably%2C%20it%20was%20the%20collapse%20of%20Bashar%20al-Assad's%20regime%20in%20Syria%20in%20early%20December%20that%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20key%20impetus%20to%20the%20strengthening%20of%20ties%20between%20Tehran%20and%20Moscow.%20Both%20powers%20lost%20a%20key%20ally%20in%20al-Assad%2C%20weakening%20their%20power%20in%20the%20wider%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737985080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F3jn64sug_sukhoi-35-reuters_625x300_27_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Firan-adds-russian-made-sukhoi-35-fighter-jets-to-