s%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20Claude%20AI%20in%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20DeepSeek%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20is%20an%20advanced%20AI%20model%20developed%20by%20a%20Hangzhou-based%20research%20lab%20of%20the%20same%20name.%20It%20was%20founded%20in%202023%20by%20Liang%20Wenfeng%2C%20an%20engineer%20with%20a%20background%20in%20AI%20and%20quantitative%20finance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20DeepSeek-V3%20model%2C%20an%20advanced%20open-source%20AI%20system%2C%20it%20surpassed%20OpenAI's%20ChatGPT%20to%20become%20the%20top-rated%20free%20app%20on%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20in%20several%20countries%2C%20including%20the%20US%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20China.%20DeepSeek's%20rise%20to%20prominence%20made%20a%20splash%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%2C%20challenging%20the%20belief%20that%20the%20US%20held%20a%20dominant%20position%20in%20this%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20latest%20release%2C%20R1%2C%20rivals%20industry%20leaders%20such%20as%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%20but%20stands%20out%20for%20being%20cost-efficient%2C%20open%20source%2C%20and%20offering%20unlimited%20free%20usage.%20It%20enables%20high-performance%20AI%20access%20without%20the%20steep%20costs%20typically%20associated%20with%20such%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20is%20DeepSeek%20different%20from%20OpenAI%20and%20Meta%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek%20sets%20itself%20apart%20from%20competitors%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Meta%20by%20focusing%20on%20affordability%20and%20efficiency.%20While%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Meta%20develop%20highly%20advanced%20models%20that%20require%20significant%20resources%20and%20expensive%20AI%20chips%20(like%20Nvidia's%20H100%20GPUs)%2C%20DeepSeek%20has%20created%20models%20that%20perform%20similarly%20but%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%20DeepSeek's%20use%20of%20more%20affordable%20AI%20hardware%20and%20innovative%20approaches%20to%20model%20training%20enables%20it%20to%20compete%20with%20the%20big%20players%20while%20keeping%20costs%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20chatbot%20app%20also%20offers%20unique%20features%2C%20such%20as%20articulating%20its%20reasoning%20before%20responding%2C%20distinguishing%20it%20from%20OpenAI's%20models%20like%20ChatGPT.%20This%20open-source%20approach%20allows%20developers%20to%20build%20on%20DeepSeek's%20technology%2C%20a%20key%20part%20of%20its%20appeal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20DeepSeek%20gaining%20attention%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20key%20reason%20for%20the%20buzz%20around%20DeepSeek%20is%20that%20the%20Chinese%20AI%20assistant%20is%20free%2C%20unlimited%2C%20and%20open-source.%20It%20is%20celebrated%20for%20its%20transparency%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20ability%20to%20make%20AI%20accessible%20to%20everyone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepSeek's%20breakthrough%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20US%20has%20placed%20restrictions%20on%20advanced%20semiconductor%20exports%20to%20China%2C%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20limiting%20China's%20ability%20to%20advance%20in%20AI.%20DeepSeek%20has%20managed%20to%20work%20around%20these%20restrictions%20by%20developing%20models%20that%20require%20fewer%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20has%20sparked%20concern%20in%20the%20US%2C%20where%20tech%20giants%20Nvidia%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20have%20heavily%20invested%20in%20AI%20infrastructure%20that%20may%20soon%20face%20increased%20competition%20from%20low-cost%20alternatives%20like%20DeepSeek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImpact%20on%20US%20stocks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20DeepSeek%20has%20had%20an%20immediate%20effect%20on%20stock%20markets.%20Shares%20of%20major%20US%20AI-related%20companies%2C%20including%20Nvidia%2C%20Meta%2C%20and%20Microsoft%2C%20dropped%20in%20response%20to%20DeepSeek's%20success.%20Analysts%20have%20warned%20that%20the%20rise%20of%20low-cost%20Chinese%20alternatives%20to%20established%20US%20AI%20models%20could%20disrupt%20the%20investment%20landscape%2C%20forcing%20companies%20to%20reconsider%20their%20AI%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20DeepSeek%20continues%20to%20gain%20traction%2C%20other%20companies%20in%20the%20AI%20supply%20chain%2C%20such%20as%20chipmakers%20and%20AI%20hardware%20manufacturers%2C%20may%20see%20their%20profits%20squeezed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737982920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Ffptb8778_deepseek_625x300_27_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-what-makes-chinas-deepseek-a-game-changer-in-ai-7571661%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Artificial%20Intelligence%20(AI)%20is%20constantly%20evolving%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20new%20player%20in%20the%20market.DeepSeek%2C%20a%20new%20AI%20model%20from%20China%2C%20has%20captured%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20tech%20world%2C%20surpassing%20the%20likes%20of%20ChatGPT%2C%20Gemini%2C%20and%20Claude%20AI%20in%20performance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fexplained-what-makes-chinas-deepseek-a-game-changer-in-ai-7571661%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Entrepreneur%20Transforms%20Industrial%20Plastic%20Waste%20into%20Rs%201.3%20Crore%20Eco-Friendly%20Packaging%20Venture%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20tops%20the%20global%20list%20in%20plastic%20waste%20generation%2C%20producing%20a%20staggering%2010.2%20million%20tonnes%20annually.%20This%20figure%20is%20more%20than%20double%20that%20of%20the%20next%20biggest%20polluters%2C%20including%20Pakistan%2C%20Bangladesh%2C%20and%20Russia.%20And%20tackling%20this%20head%20on%20is%20Mohd%20Suhail%2C%20a%2032-year-old%20entrepreneur%20from%20Delhi%2C%20who%20has%20managed%20to%20stop%20200%20tons%20of%20industrial%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F3556