continue%20till%20it%20appears%20good%20in%20photographs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuch%20people%20cannot%20benefit%20the%20country.%20Our%20faith%20is%20in%20God%20--%20people%20perform%20'puja'%20at%20home%20every%20day%2C%20all%20women%20step%20out%20of%20their%20homes%20after%20performing%20'puja'%2C%20there%20is%20no%20issue.%20But%20we%20have%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20poor%20being%20exploited%20in%20the%20name%20of%20religion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kharge%20said.%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20also%20present%20at%20the%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20on%20a%20day%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20took%20a%20holy%20dip%20at%20the%20Triveni%20Sangam%20in%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20president's%20remarks%20have%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20BJP.%20Party%20MP%20and%20spokesperson%20Sambit%20Patra%20said%20the%20Congress's%20hatred%20was%20an%20attack%20on%20the%20faith%20of%20crores%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMahakumbh%20has%20been%20the%20symbol%20of%20the%20Sanatana%20faith%20for%20ages.%20I%20am%20pained%20to%20say%20that%20while%20the%20entire%20world%20reveres%20this%20faith%2C%20the%20biggest%20opposition%20party%20in%20India%20is%20ridiculing%20the%20Mahakumbh%20and%20this%20faith.%20They%20are%20making%20a%20mockery%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patra%20said%20the%20Congress%20president's%20remarks%20on%20the%20Mahakumbh%20and%20Ganga%20have%20hurt%20crores.%20%26quot%3BHe%20questioned%20if%20taking%20a%20dip%20in%20the%20Ganga%20would%20remove%20poverty%2C%20provide%20jobs%2C%20or%20bring%20happiness%20to%20the%20people.%20I%20challenge%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20to%20make%20such%20remarks%20about%20any%20other%20religion's%20faith.%20Can%20they%20question%20if%20people%20get%20jobs%20or%20if%20poverty%20is%20alleviated%20by%20