er%20to%20take%20more%20than%2070%20Test%20wickets%20in%20a%20calendar%20year%20after%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%2C%20Anil%20Kumble%20and%20Kapil%20Dev.%20Those%20numbers%20were%20enough%20for%20him%20to%20beat%20competition%20from%20Sri%20Lanka's%20Kamindu%20Mendis%20and%20England%20batting%20duo%20of%20Harry%20Brook%2C%20and%20Joe%20Root%20to%20win%20the%20prestigious%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20year%20where%20Bumrah%20excelled%20in%20both%20home%20and%20away%20conditions%2C%20proving%20to%20be%20a%20key%20contributor%20in%20keeping%20India%20in%20contention%20for%20a%20spot%20in%20the%202025%20World%20Test%20Championship%20Final%2C%20though%20the%20side%20fell%20short%20of%20making%20it%20to%20the%20title%20clash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20incredible%202024%20began%20during%20India's%20memorable%20Test%20win%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20Cape%20Town%2C%20where%20he%20picked%20eight%20wickets.%20He%20then%20went%20on%20to%20bag%2019%20wickets%20in%20India%20beating%20England%204-1%20margin%2C%20with%20the%20highlight%20being%20a%20match%20haul%20of%20nine%20wickets%20and%20helping%20India%20to%20a%20series-levelling%20win%20in%20Visakhapatnam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah's%20most%20standout%20performance%20in%20Tests%20in%202024%20came%20in%20the%20high-stakes%20Border-Gavaskar%20Trophy%20Series%20in%20Australia%2C%20where%20he%20picked%2032%20wickets%20in%20five%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2013.06%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%2028.37%20to%20clinch%20the%20Player%20of%20the%20Series%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20during%20the%20series%20in%20Australia%20that%20Bumrah%20crossed%20the%20200%20Test%20wickets%20milestone%2C%20becoming%20the%2012th%20Indian%20bowler%20to%20do%20so%2C%20though%20it%20didn't%20help%20the%20visitors%20in%20avoiding%20a%203-1%20series%20defeat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20best%20performance%20on%20tour%20of%20Australia%20came%20when%20he%20picked%20eight%20wickets%20in%20a%20stunning%20spell%20in%20Perth%2C%20including%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20in%20the%20first%20innings%2C%20to%20lift%20India%20towards%20a%20295-run%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBumrah%2C%2031%2C%20also%20set%20a%20unique%20record%20while%20achieving%20the%20feat%2C%20becoming%20the%20only%20bowler%20in%20Test%20history%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%20200%20dismissals%20to%20have%20an%20average%20less%20than%2020%20(19.4).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737974100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fe3joh8g_jasprit-bumrah_625x300_03_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjasprit-bumrah-named-icc-mens-test-cricketer-of-the-year-for-2024-7570395%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Indias%20fast-bowling%20spearhead%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20named%20as%20the%20winner%20of%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Test%20Cricketer%20of%20the%20Year%20award%20for%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fjasprit-bumrah-named-icc-mens-test-cricketer-of-the-year-for-2024-7570395%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20How%20Kumbh%20Inspires%20India's%20Leadership%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20vast%20landscape%20of%20human%20gatherings%2C%20nothing%20quite%20compares%20to%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela.%20As%20a%20company%2C%20the%20Adani%20Group%20is%20still%20deeply%20engaged%20this%20year%20in%20the%20Mela%2C%20and%2C%20every%20single%20time%20I%20have%20a%20discussion%20on%20this%20subject%2C%20I%20am%20humbled%20by%20the%20vision%20our%20forefathers%20had.%20As%20someone%20who%20has%20built%20ports%2C%20airports%20and%20energy%20networks%20across%20India%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20astonished%20by%20this%20magnificent%20demonstration%20of%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3Bspiritual%20infrastructure%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20a%20force%20that%20has%20sustained%20our%20civilisation%20for%20millennia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2vq6m5to_adani_625x300_27_January_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EProbably%20The%20World's%20Largest%20Management%20Case%20Study%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Harvard%20Business%20School%20studied%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela's%20logistics%2C%20they%20marvelled%20at%20its%20scale.%20But%2C%20as%20an%20Indian%2C%20I%20see%20something%20deeper%3A%20the%20world's%20most%20successful%20pop-up%20megacity%20isn't%20just%20about%20numbers%2C%20it's%20about%20eternal%20principles%20that%20we%20at%20the%20Adani%20Group%20strive%20to%20embrace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsider%20this%3A%20every%2012%20years%2C%20a%20temporary%20city%20larger%20than%20New%20York%20materialises%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20sacred%20rivers.%20No%20board%20meetings.%20No%20PowerPoint%20presentations.%20No%20venture%20capital.%20Just%20pure%2C%20time-tested%20Indian%20%3Cem%3Ejugaad%20%3C%2Fem%3E(innovation)%20backed%20by%20centuries%20of%20iterative%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Three%20Indestructible%20Pillars%20of%20Kumbh%20Leadership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Scale%20with%20Soul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Kumbh%2C%20scale%20isn't%20just%20about%20size%20%E2%80%93%20it's%20about%20impact.%20When%20200%20million%20people%20gather%20with%20dedication%20and%20service%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20an%20event%20but%20a%20unique%20confluence%20of%20souls.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20call%20%26quot%3Bspiritual%20economies%20of%20scale%26quot%3B.%20The%20larger%20it%20grows%2C%20the%20more%20efficient%20it%20becomes%2C%20not%20just%20materially%20but%20in%20human%20and%20humanity%20terms.%20True%20scale%20is%20not%20measured%20in%20metrics%20but%20in%20the%20moments%20of%20unity%20it%20creates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F85fa2lhg_adank_625x300_27_January_25.jpeg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Sustainable%20Before%20Sustainability%20Was%20Cool%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELong%20before%20'ESG'%20became%20a%20boardroom%20buzzword%2C%20the%20Kumbh%20Mela%20practised%20circular%20economy%20principles.%20A%20river%20is%20not%20just%20a%20source%20of%20water%20but%20the%20flow%20of%20life.%20Preserving%20it%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20ancient%20wisdom.%20The%20same%20river%20that%20hosts%20millions%20returns%20to%20its%20natural%20state%20following%20the%20Kumbh%2C%20having%20cleansed%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20devotees%20and%20confident%20that%20it%20can%20cleanse%20itself%20of%20all%20the%20%26quot%3Bimpurities%26quot%3B%20it%20washed%20away.%20Perhaps%20there's%20a%20lesson%20here%20for%20our%20modern%20development%20paradigms.%20Progress%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20not%20in%20what%20we%20take%20from%20the%20earth%2C%20but%20in%20how%20we%20give%20back%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Leadership%20Through%20Service%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20powerful%20aspect%3F%20The%20absence%20of%20a%20single%20controlling%20authority.%20True%20leadership%20lies%20not%20in%20giving%20orders%20but%20in%20the%20ability%20to%20take%20everyone%20along.%20Various%20%3Cem%3Eakharas%20%3C%2Fem%3E(religious%20orders)%2C%20local%20authorities%20and%20volunteers%20work%20in%20harmony.%20It%20is%20leadership%20through%20service%2C%20not%20dominanc